 things in life, <strong>timing</strong> is very important on the stock\'s market, and this is exactly what Simon\'s MA indicator can help you with, timing your buying and selling stocks.</p><p>Buy in case of upward trend change, and sell when the indicator predicts fall. Profit from the difference.</p>		\n			<h3>Well...and how to track those signals?</h3>		\n		<p>Just sign up for our free weekly email alert to receive a list of Nasdaq and NYSE large companies where trend change has been detected since the previous week.</p>		\n										<img width=\"640\" height=\"307\" src=\"http://simonstockalert.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tsla-1024x491.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"http://simonstockalert.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tsla-1024x491.png 1024w, http://simonstockalert.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tsla-300x144.png 300w, http://simonstockalert.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/tsla-768x368.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />											\n			<h1>Sign up for Simon\'s MA trend indicator for FREE!</h1>		\n<form method=\"post\" action=\"http://simonstockalert.com/?na=s\" onsubmit=\"return newsletter_check(this)\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"nlang\" value=\"\">\n<label>Email address:</label><input type=\"email\" name=\"ne\" required>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"Subscribe\">\n</form>\n			<h3>Can I customize the indicator?</h3>		\n		<p>No, unfortunately not.</p>		\n			<h3>Should I buy and sell stocks based on Simon\'s stock alert alone?</h3>		\n		<p>No, you should always analyse also the underlying fundamentals before making any decisions.</p>		\n			<h3>How can I cancel the service?</h3>		\n		<p>You can cancel the newsletter any time by using the unsubscribe link.</p>		\n			<h3>Finally, can I support you in any way?</h3>		\n		<p>Yes, I appreciate any donation. </p>		\n			<form action=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr\" method=\"post\" target=\"_top\">\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"cmd\" value=\"_s-xclick\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"host